1
00:00:00,125 --> 00:00:02,083
Kungenzeka ukuthi usuzwile
ngeNcwadi kaMormoni,

2
00:00:02,083 --> 00:00:04,542
kodwa ungahle umangale ukuthi
eqinisweni imayelana nani.

3
00:00:04,542 --> 00:00:05,542
Okusobala ngayo,

4
00:00:05,542 --> 00:00:08,918
iyindaba yeminyaka eyinkulungwane
yempucuko  enkulu.

5
00:00:08,918 --> 00:00:09,876
Kodwa empeleni,

6
00:00:09,876 --> 00:00:14,542
imayelana nabantu ababephokophelele
ukufunda nokulandela uJesu Kristu.

7
00:00:14,542 --> 00:00:16,375
Iqala eJerusalema cishe
eminyakeni engama-600

8
00:00:16,375 --> 00:00:17,918
ngaphambi kokuzalwa kukaKristu lapho

9
00:00:17,918 --> 00:00:21,542
umprofethi exwayiswa nguNkulunkulu ukuba
abalekele imbubhiso eyabe iza kulo idolobha.

10
00:00:21,542 --> 00:00:23,792
Yena nomndeni wakhe baholwa
ukuba bawelele ngaphesheya

11
00:00:23,792 --> 00:00:26,000
kolwandle baye ezweni
eselaziwa ngokuthi yiMelika.

12
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:28,959
Abantu bayanda beze bahlukane
babe yizizwe ezimbili

13
00:00:28,959 --> 00:00:31,626
ezinkulu ezinezikhathi zezimpi nezokuthula.

14
00:00:31,626 --> 00:00:35,459
Izimpilo zabo zingakugqugquzela
ukuba ube nokholo kuJesu Kristu,

15
00:00:35,459 --> 00:00:38,250
ugcine imiyalelo Yakhe, futhi usize nabanye.

16
00:00:38,250 --> 00:00:43,083
INcwadi kaMormoni iqukethe amazwi angcwele
abaprofethi ababefakaza ngokuza koMsindisi.

17
00:00:43,083 --> 00:00:45,959
Iqinisekisa amaqiniso
aseBhayibhelini futhi ifakaza

18
00:00:45,959 --> 00:00:48,667
ngokuthi uJesu Kristu
uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu;

19
00:00:48,667 --> 00:00:49,918
ukuthi Waphila, Wafa,

20
00:00:49,918 --> 00:00:52,918
Wasinqobela ukufa kanye
nesono umuntu ngamunye.

21
00:00:52,918 --> 00:00:57,083
Yingakho-ke ibizwa ngokuthi “Elinye
iTestamente likaJesu Kristu.”

22
00:00:57,083 --> 00:00:57,751
Eqinisweni,

23
00:00:57,751 --> 00:01:01,459
isigigaba esikhulu sale ncwadi
wukuvakasha kukaJesu Kristu

24
00:01:01,459 --> 00:01:05,417
kubantu basemazweni aseMelika
emva kovuko Lwakhe eJerusalema.

25
00:01:05,417 --> 00:01:10,125
Ufundisa ivangeli Lakhe, ulapha abagulayo,
futhi ubusisa nabantwana babo.

26
00:01:10,125 --> 00:01:12,459
Kodwa lokho kuseyisiqalo nje sendaba.

27
00:01:12,459 --> 00:01:15,417
Umthelela wangempela
weNcwadi kaMormoni wukuthi

28
00:01:15,417 --> 00:01:19,000
ingakusiza kanjani ezinseleleni
obhekene nazo namuhla.

29
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:21,000
Ungathola induduzo, ukuqondiswa,

30
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:25,209
futhi ufunde nokuthi ungaba kanjani
ngumuntu ongcono nonenjabulo.

31
00:01:25,209 --> 00:01:26,626
Ngaphezu kwakho konke,

32
00:01:26,626 --> 00:01:30,083
ungasondelana kakhulu
noMsindisi wakho uJesu Kristu.

